text: Aalesunds Socialdemokrat (The Ålesund Social Democrat) was a newspaper published in Ålesund, Norway from 1908 to 1910.Høeg, Tom Arbo. 1974. Norske aviser: Registerbind. Oslo: Universitetsbibliotekets Hustrykkeri, pp. 79, 118.Thorson, Odd. 1952. Ålesund 1848-1948: økonomisk og kommunal historie, vol. 2. Oslo, p. 182. The newspaper was a successor of another paper, called Nybrot. The editorial team consisted of Julius Berge and Elias Røsvik.Adressebog for Romsdals amt met skatteligninger. 1909. Kristiania: S. M.
